snippet.title: Key Hunters DX - ARE U UP 4 IT?
snippet.description:
ARE U UP FOR IT? Vector from the Chaotix joins the Hunt in Key Hunters DX!

The Sonic Fangame that takes a classic spin on the treasure hunting stages from the Adventure games and creates a brand new experience for everyone to enjoy!

Follow our Twitter/X Page for more updates and news on the project!
Twitter: @sonicandknuk
